We are not holy people, we are yet full of
lots of greed and lust, but they are above

00:30:03.590 --> 00:30:04.590
everything.

00:30:04.590 --> 00:30:08.120
So, when we are discussing them, we have to
know, we have to do it with great shraddha,

00:30:08.120 --> 00:30:15.300
and with our head bowed before them that it
is our luck and we are very fortunate that

00:30:15.300 --> 00:30:22.370
we have been able to learn something about
these two Primordial Parents who have brought

00:30:22.370 --> 00:30:28.480
forth this Creation, their child.

00:30:28.480 --> 00:30:39.280
So, one of these then again cracks and becomes
a surya-mandal, and a surya-mandala has got,

00:30:39.280 --> 00:30:46.920
as you know, Earth and Moon and all these
things and I have told you how Earth is created.

00:30:46.920 --> 00:30:57.010
After the Creation of Earth, first, you know
that amino-acids were formed, the vegetation

00:30:57.010 --> 00:31:00.460
started and then the human being started.

00:31:00.460 --> 00:31:04.990
Now, the matter, also, is a very systematic
thing.

00:31:04.990 --> 00:31:09.270
Matter is not unsystematic, it is systematic,
but it is not organised – there is difference

00:31:09.270 --> 00:31:10.441
between the two.

00:31:10.441 --> 00:31:12.970
The systematic things are dead, can be dead.

00:31:12.970 --> 00:31:19.920
You can put five stones here in a systematic
manner, but they are not organised, because

00:31:19.920 --> 00:31:20.980
they are not living things.

00:31:20.980 --> 00:31:22.830
There’s a difference between the two.

00:31:22.830 --> 00:31:25.990
So, first, the systematic things were laid
down.

00:31:25.990 --> 00:31:35.750
Perhaps, if you know about the…Eight different
types of elements were created.

00:31:35.750 --> 00:31:44.420
These were created and were put into proper
places through Shri Ganesha.

00:31:44.420 --> 00:31:57.250
You know that the carbon… carbon is in the
centre of these periodical elements that appear.

00:31:57.250 --> 00:32:04.790
That means a element which has got one valency,
two valency, three valency and four valency,

00:32:04.790 --> 00:32:09.880
the three are the plus ones, then you’ve
got one C, carbon, which has got four valences.

00:32:09.880 --> 00:32:18.430
Then you have got, again, minus one, two,
three and four – is a complete eight.

00:32:18.430 --> 00:32:25.600
Like that, the whole matter has been organised.

00:32:25.600 --> 00:32:32.830
To organise the matter, some deity was to
be created for that, and first deity that

00:32:32.830 --> 00:32:35.600
was created was that of Shri Ganesh.

00:32:35.600 --> 00:32:45.140
Let us see now how She created here.

00:32:45.140 --> 00:32:54.930
You have seen that one part of Her, which
is the Mahasaraswati, has created the matter.

00:32:54.930 --> 00:32:59.180
Mahasaraswati has created the matter.

00:32:59.180 --> 00:33:02.980
Now, Mahakali has to give them existence.

00:33:02.980 --> 00:33:04.550
How do you get an existence?

00:33:04.550 --> 00:33:09.090
Is through your sustenance or, you can say,
through your quality – whatever you are.

00:33:09.090 --> 00:33:18.010
So, Mahakali gives that existence to those
material things, not human beings or living

00:33:18.010 --> 00:33:32.400
things but matter, through a deity known as
Shri Ganesh.

00:33:32.400 --> 00:33:38.290
Mahakali…

00:33:38.290 --> 00:33:42.590
In the heart of the Viraata, as you see, – you’ll
see Viraata also He comes in, because that

00:33:42.590 --> 00:33:48.200
I will tell you later on – but in the heart
of Viraata, is the Primordial Being, the complete

00:33:48.200 --> 00:33:51.309
Primordial Being, the Mahakali is settled
down.

00:33:51.309 --> 00:33:57.040
What She does, She goes three and a half from
the heart: one up, one down like that – three

00:33:57.040 --> 00:34:01.510
and a half times and comes to the end of the
three and a half, down-way.

00:34:01.510 --> 00:34:03.710
Three and a half.

00:34:03.710 --> 00:34:06.030
Now, She comes at the end of it.

00:34:06.030 --> 00:34:11.090
And if you put three and a half like that
and if you cut it straight, you get 7 centres

00:34:11.090 --> 00:34:12.460
cut in.

