Is there a drawing person who knows how to
draw?

00:34:25.220 --> 00:34:39.380
You should start from like that, you can put
it like this.

00:34:39.380 --> 00:34:44.550
She comes down here.

00:34:44.550 --> 00:34:50.730
She comes down here and from here She penetrates.

00:34:50.730 --> 00:34:55.440
You see, She cuts at seven points here.

00:34:55.440 --> 00:35:01.720
At this point, She creates the first deity,
little below, of Shri Ganesh.

00:35:01.720 --> 00:35:06.340
I mean, this is not done in one day, is not
done in one year, not done in one Yuga, it

00:35:06.340 --> 00:35:07.920
is done in many Kalpas.

00:35:07.920 --> 00:35:16.100
The first step is to create Shri Ganesh, this
is Her abode and She puts Shri Ganesh.

00:35:16.100 --> 00:35:20.950
Now, he is emitting his vibrations through
all this.

00:35:20.950 --> 00:35:25.220
He passes through all this whatever She has
created.

00:35:25.220 --> 00:35:31.050
On this picture is settled the work of the
Mahasaraswati, you can say.

00:35:31.050 --> 00:35:35.619
She comes down with all Her programs like
this and She makes it.

00:35:35.619 --> 00:35:37.119
And She gets joined here again.

00:35:37.119 --> 00:35:40.790
So, Shri Ganesh emits His vibrations through
her.

00:35:40.790 --> 00:35:46.120
First, Shri Mahakali creates Shri Ganesh and
then Mahasaraswati comes down, She creates

00:35:46.120 --> 00:35:49.570
all these things and gets connected to Shri
Ganesh.

00:35:49.570 --> 00:35:56.740
So, the vibrations of Shri Ganesh start flowing
through all the creation of Mahasaraswati.

00:35:56.740 --> 00:36:05.720
Before creating all this, the complete thought
of what is going to happen in future comes

00:36:05.720 --> 00:36:10.160
in a clear-cut vision of the Adi Shakti.

00:36:10.160 --> 00:36:11.890
And She puts Her plans through.

00:36:11.890 --> 00:36:17.270
First of all, the Mahalakshmi power comes
down and creates the Shri Ganesh.

00:36:17.270 --> 00:36:22.360
You can understand now how important it is
that we have to be holy people.

00:36:22.360 --> 00:36:25.760
First, She created the holiness on this Earth.

00:36:25.760 --> 00:36:30.170
First thing, Her relationship with the child
was established, because the Creation is going

00:36:30.170 --> 00:36:33.750
to be created in the image of Her child.

00:36:33.750 --> 00:36:40.230
That’s why Shri Ganesh was created first.

00:36:40.230 --> 00:36:45.619
And then from here, say, is the Adi Shakti,
the other power, Mahasaraswati, on Her way,

00:36:45.619 --> 00:36:48.670
She comes down and gets connected with Shri
Ganesh.

00:36:48.670 --> 00:36:53.810
And that’s how the Shri Ganesh establishes
the relationship and emits His vibrations

00:36:53.810 --> 00:36:54.810
through this.

00:36:54.810 --> 00:36:58.740
Because of His vibrations passing through
the matter that She has created.

