Nobody has seen the axis, but they say, there
is an axis, from the way it moves.

00:37:10.270 --> 00:37:11.720
There is a kind of an axis.

00:37:11.720 --> 00:37:19.020
Now, this is the power of Mahakali passing
through the [axis].

00:37:19.020 --> 00:37:23.390
We can say, it’s the power of Shri Ganesh
passing through the axis of the Mother Earth,

00:37:23.390 --> 00:37:25.940
which has got magnetic power in it.

00:37:25.940 --> 00:37:32.380
And that’s how, through that, it controls
its speed, its movement, and also it looks

00:37:32.380 --> 00:37:33.380
after us.

