You just put your head on the soil, put your
both the hands on the Mother Earth and you’ll

00:38:16.660 --> 00:38:19.240
find the whole thing will be sucked out from
your forehead.

00:38:19.240 --> 00:38:23.940
It has been done with many, even from the
legs it can take out.

00:38:23.940 --> 00:38:28.810
Mother Earth is actually, is the Mother of
Adi Shakti, you can say.

00:38:28.810 --> 00:38:34.661
She is the Mother, they say, because She is
made in such a way that She takes all the

00:38:34.661 --> 00:38:37.340
weights of the world in Herself.

00:38:37.340 --> 00:38:40.961
She controls all the weights of the world
and She can consume all your weight.

00:38:40.961 --> 00:38:41.961
She’s the dharaa.

00:38:41.961 --> 00:38:47.040
Now, weight means everything that… your
weight is what we weigh in: that’s not the

00:38:47.040 --> 00:38:48.040
thing.

