And then some other deity has to, like Vishnu
himself, has to come on this Earth to save

00:39:07.540 --> 00:39:11.170
Her from this too much of overloading of sins
upon this Earth.

00:39:11.170 --> 00:39:12.170
Is a fact!

00:39:12.170 --> 00:39:14.350
It is not I’m telling you a mythical story,
is a fact.

00:39:14.350 --> 00:39:16.920
Which you have to verify after getting vibrations.

