Actually, it was Her mere desire which brought
forth these.

00:40:41.560 --> 00:40:46.620
For us it is impossible to understand someone
like that, who, just by mere desire can create.

00:40:46.620 --> 00:40:51.880
But when we think of somebody who is above
all the powers of the world, the One the,

00:40:51.880 --> 00:40:55.090
who is the highest of all: She can do anything
She feels like.

00:40:55.090 --> 00:40:56.740
Can’t we think like that?

00:40:56.740 --> 00:40:58.560
We cannot think of someone like that.

00:40:58.560 --> 00:41:02.320
We think of God, who is Almighty, we call
Him, but when we talk of His mights we start

00:41:02.320 --> 00:41:03.320
laughing.

00:41:03.320 --> 00:41:04.320
How can it be?

00:41:04.320 --> 00:41:05.320
But She can do anything She wants to.

00:41:05.320 --> 00:41:10.220
It is only Her mere desire that has brought
forth all these creations and all this things

00:41:10.220 --> 00:41:13.270
that you see in this world are created only
by Her desire.

00:41:13.270 --> 00:41:14.830
She created akasha.

00:41:14.830 --> 00:41:20.190
She created all these five elements, which
you know, and then She started Her another

00:41:20.190 --> 00:41:23.430
form which we call as the Mahalakshmi form.

00:41:23.430 --> 00:41:28.930
Before that, I think, I should tell you about
Shri Ganesha’s existence in the matter.

00:41:28.930 --> 00:41:33.150
He acts in the matter as vibrations, as Mahasaraswati
vibrations.

00:41:33.150 --> 00:41:38.310
They are electromagnetic vibrations, Mahasaraswati
vibrations are electromagnetic vibrations,

00:41:38.310 --> 00:41:43.610
we can say, that electromagnetic and also
there is sound, and all these five elements

00:41:43.610 --> 00:41:44.690
are expressed in that.

00:41:44.690 --> 00:41:54.590
You can record them – because if you take
a sulphur dioxide, for example, a sulphur

00:41:54.590 --> 00:42:00.369
dioxide and two oxygen and one sulphur and
if you watch them properly under a very highly

00:42:00.369 --> 00:42:05.820
micro – you can try, I don’t know if people
have tried, but you can try to find out – and

00:42:05.820 --> 00:42:13.160
put it under, let’s say, a very highly developed
micro – microwave- microscope, you can say,

00:42:13.160 --> 00:42:20.670
you can see that the oxygen things and sulphur,
– sulphur is stationary, – but these two

00:42:20.670 --> 00:42:21.670
are vibrating.

00:42:21.670 --> 00:42:25.120
They are vibrating, there’s a vibration
going between these bonds.

00:42:25.120 --> 00:42:30.810
They can be isometric also, they can be symmetric,
they can be even, uneven and they can be expanding,

00:42:30.810 --> 00:42:32.080
and closing like that.

00:42:32.080 --> 00:42:35.280
So, there are three types of vibrations, we
find.

00:42:35.280 --> 00:42:38.351
And the fourth side is nothing but Shri Ganesha
himself who is controlling.

00:42:38.351 --> 00:42:42.940
So, this we can see with our naked eyes, if
you want to see, even if you are realised

00:42:42.940 --> 00:42:43.940
or not.

00:42:43.940 --> 00:42:47.970
From where do these vibrations come in the
minutest paramanu, as you call, the molecules?

00:42:47.970 --> 00:42:53.980
In a molecule, how do you get these vibrations,
can you explain this?

00:42:53.980 --> 00:42:57.220
It is so much, sukshma, parasukshma.

00:42:57.220 --> 00:43:04.630
The powers of Ganesha are very, very subtle
and they enter into the matter and create

00:43:04.630 --> 00:43:11.570
this kind of vibrations, which you can even
see and record, electromagnetic vibrations,

00:43:11.570 --> 00:43:18.470
in, even, a one small, little molecule.

00:43:18.470 --> 00:43:25.800
So, we have in these, as I told you, into
the periodic level, periodic laws of elements,

00:43:25.800 --> 00:43:28.890
you can find out that all the elements are
divided into eight types.

00:43:28.890 --> 00:43:30.150
Just see!

00:43:30.150 --> 00:43:34.480
How can all the elements be divided into eight
parts without somebody being there?

00:43:34.480 --> 00:43:40.430
Can you do something without organising a
proper chart of these elements?

00:43:40.430 --> 00:43:43.270
Just think about it!

00:43:43.270 --> 00:43:46.040
You see, when we challenge God, we have to
understand that in this world everything is

00:43:46.040 --> 00:43:51.440
so well organised, there are eight elements
spread out so well, placed so well.

00:43:51.440 --> 00:43:56.800
And it has a particular style of behaviour
and every element is different in numbers

00:43:56.800 --> 00:44:04.110
and protons and these numbers are very well
calculated in such a manner that the end of

00:44:04.110 --> 00:44:10.890
it, that the last circle, that the last circle
of all the protons should be eight.

00:44:10.890 --> 00:44:17.130
If it is not eight, if it is less than eight
then it creates a valency problem.

00:44:17.130 --> 00:44:20.820
It is so well organised, then, even if you
study this, if there is anybody who knows

00:44:20.820 --> 00:44:24.540
little bit of chemistry, you know, so if you
know chemistry, it’s such a wonderful thing.

00:44:24.540 --> 00:44:25.540
We take it for granted!

00:44:25.540 --> 00:44:28.619
We think it is our right to have the matter
so well organised for us!

00:44:28.619 --> 00:44:33.760
But the valencies are all depending on such
a nice organisation of this eight protons

00:44:33.760 --> 00:44:36.200
at the outer thing.

00:44:36.200 --> 00:44:37.770
This is all done through the Mahasaraswati
power.

00:44:37.770 --> 00:44:43.650
But the vibrating force…Now see, there is
a vibrating force: this is all done through

00:44:43.650 --> 00:44:46.020
the, as I told you, through the Mahasaraswati
power.

00:44:46.020 --> 00:44:47.609
She creates.

00:44:47.609 --> 00:44:51.040
Now the vibrating force: He exists, matter
also exists.

00:44:51.040 --> 00:44:52.040
It must exist.

00:44:52.040 --> 00:44:53.880
If it does not exist, nothing can exist.

00:44:53.880 --> 00:45:01.310
So, the existence force is given through the
Mahakali force, which is acting through Shri

00:45:01.310 --> 00:45:04.670
Ganesh, who is sitting at the nucleus.

00:45:04.670 --> 00:45:08.970
He is sitting at the nucleus of every [atom].

00:45:08.970 --> 00:45:13.660
Can you imagine how much it must be?

00:45:13.660 --> 00:45:17.330
Every molecule and every atom.

00:45:17.330 --> 00:45:19.200
You cannot understand the finiteness of it.

00:45:19.200 --> 00:45:22.790
Now, see, say, take one element like gold,
how many molecules it has?

00:45:22.790 --> 00:45:23.820
Can you calculate?

00:45:23.820 --> 00:45:25.320
[It’s] beyond us!

00:45:25.320 --> 00:45:28.690
How many, you can say, atoms it has?

00:45:28.690 --> 00:45:30.970
We just cannot calculate it.

00:45:30.970 --> 00:45:34.320
And then how many Ganesha’s pictures must
be there?

00:45:34.320 --> 00:45:36.050
How is it achieved?

00:45:36.050 --> 00:45:42.240
Is another thing which I will tell you if
I come in the way.

00:45:42.240 --> 00:45:50.490
How infinite reflections are caught into and
why there are two things like Shiva and Adi

00:45:50.490 --> 00:45:51.490
Shakti?

00:45:51.490 --> 00:45:54.990
The reason is it has to create an infinite
reflection.

00:45:54.990 --> 00:45:57.250
How do you create an infinite reflection?

00:45:57.250 --> 00:45:59.260
Do you know that?

00:45:59.260 --> 00:46:05.500
Anybody who knows physics?

00:46:05.500 --> 00:46:10.170
If you place in the centre of two mirrors
something, then the reflections are infinite.

00:46:10.170 --> 00:46:20.980
So, the first mirror is the Adi Shakti and
the second mirror is this Creation, and that’s

00:46:20.980 --> 00:46:27.030
how you can get infinite reflections on this
Earth.

00:46:27.030 --> 00:46:29.640
This is the reason why you can get infinite
reflections.

00:46:29.640 --> 00:46:37.540
And that’s why you had to create another
one who reflects it.

00:46:37.540 --> 00:46:42.990
And that’s why there have to be three identities,
one, the God Almighty, then Adi Shakti and

00:46:42.990 --> 00:46:44.470
then the whole Universe.

00:46:44.470 --> 00:46:48.650
It had to be that way, otherwise you cannot
create infinite reflections.

00:46:48.650 --> 00:46:53.680
Now, somebody who has done this job must be
a very clever man, no doubt.

00:46:53.680 --> 00:46:58.410
When human beings think that they can know
God through their buddhi, they must know,

00:46:58.410 --> 00:47:01.910
how can you reach this Buddhi, it’s supreme.

00:47:01.910 --> 00:47:06.830
How much labour He has taken to create us!

00:47:06.830 --> 00:47:16.830
After creating the matter, then He, or I should
say, His power as Mahalakshmi descends on

00:47:16.830 --> 00:47:18.890
this Earth.

00:47:18.890 --> 00:47:23.030
Mahalakshmi helps in sustenance.

00:47:23.030 --> 00:47:27.570
Sustenance means all the scanning of all these
elements.

00:47:27.570 --> 00:47:36.080
When they create the matter, the matter is
differently created, created for different

00:47:36.080 --> 00:47:37.450
purposes.

00:47:37.450 --> 00:47:43.030
Now, what is the ultimate?

00:47:43.030 --> 00:47:48.950
The Creation has its ultimate aim is to create
human beings – this creation, just imagine!

00:47:48.950 --> 00:47:54.820
You people are so great that for you all these
troubles have been taken.

00:47:54.820 --> 00:48:00.380
Such an important thing is a human being that
all these troubles are taken, – all matter,

00:48:00.380 --> 00:48:05.520
all, everything, is used just to create you.

00:48:05.520 --> 00:48:06.520
This is the ultimate aim.

00:48:06.520 --> 00:48:12.570
Sort of a stage has to be laid down and you
come, the Sahaja Yogis come on the scene,

00:48:12.570 --> 00:48:14.869
you can say.

00:48:14.869 --> 00:48:17.000
Just the instrument of man is to be created.

00:48:17.000 --> 00:48:20.910
Now, why God wanted to create an instrument
of man?

00:48:20.910 --> 00:48:29.510
Because He wanted to create an instrument
which could feel Him, which could understand

00:48:29.510 --> 00:48:36.440
Him, which could emit, like Krishna creating
his murli (flute).

00:48:36.440 --> 00:48:41.000
He just wanted to play through our instruments
His power.

00:48:41.000 --> 00:48:46.590
But He didn’t want to do it through the
dead instruments like these but through the

00:48:46.590 --> 00:48:47.590
living instruments.

00:48:47.590 --> 00:48:54.710
Supposing, if this (microphone) can understand,
can love, has a human mind, and if my voice

00:48:54.710 --> 00:49:03.200
is passing through it like a hollow personality
then we can say that this is a realised personality.

00:49:03.200 --> 00:49:05.950
But this is not a living being, you are a
living being.

00:49:05.950 --> 00:49:10.390
You are made specially with all these difficulties
for millions of years, have been worked out

00:49:10.390 --> 00:49:14.420
so carefully, so delicately, one after another.

00:49:14.420 --> 00:49:19.740
We have to now jump to the evolution part,
because you see, it’s a very long thing.

00:49:19.740 --> 00:49:22.000
Shri Mataji: Kiti wasle (Marathi: what time
is it?)

00:49:22.000 --> 00:49:23.260
Yogi: Saha wasle (six o’clock)

00:49:23.260 --> 00:49:28.450
So, now we have to come to the most important
part which is evolution, which we should understand,

00:49:28.450 --> 00:49:35.840
because we know evolution through science.

00:49:35.840 --> 00:49:44.950
When these three forces came into being, before
creating any earth or before creating this

00:49:44.950 --> 00:49:52.840
universe or anything, first they had to draw
out a proper picture about it and a proper

00:49:52.840 --> 00:49:54.210
understanding of it, you see.

00:49:54.210 --> 00:49:56.460
As before doing anything, say, we have to
plan out things, we have a planning commission,

00:49:56.460 --> 00:49:59.490
first of all, we sit down with a planning
commission.

00:49:59.490 --> 00:50:05.030
In the same way, first, they had to form a
stage where they just plan out the things.

00:50:05.030 --> 00:50:08.349
This stage we can call it as the vaikuntha
state.

00:50:08.349 --> 00:50:13.500
Because this (current stage) is not the earliest
state, this is created later on.

00:50:13.500 --> 00:50:23.300
First, the planning state is known as the
vaikuntha state.

00:50:23.300 --> 00:50:27.020
At this stage they created all the incarnations.

00:50:27.020 --> 00:50:32.490
Incarnations were not created after the Earth
has been created, which is a very wrong idea.

00:50:32.490 --> 00:50:36.020
They created all the incarnations at the vaikuntha
state.

00:50:36.020 --> 00:50:41.820
Where you or I never existed at that time,
this Earth never existed and nothing existed

00:50:41.820 --> 00:50:43.940
that you see with your naked eyes now.

00:50:43.940 --> 00:50:49.860
But a state of existence, the first one, known
as the vaikuntha state, existed.

00:50:49.860 --> 00:50:59.470
In that vaikuntha state the planning of the
whole Universe and the whole cosmos and all

00:50:59.470 --> 00:51:00.590
that was decided.

00:51:00.590 --> 00:51:08.290
So, the first person who had to come on this
was Shiva, because without him nothing can

00:51:08.290 --> 00:51:13.540
exist, but where to settle Him down, because
He is to be reflected onto something.

00:51:13.540 --> 00:51:18.160
If Shiva has to be reflected onto someone,
you have to create a reflector.

00:51:18.160 --> 00:51:28.590
So, they had to, first, think of the one Primordial
Being or a, one Huge Identity you can call

00:51:28.590 --> 00:51:30.220
it, known as Viraat.

00:51:30.220 --> 00:51:32.760
They created Viraata.

00:51:32.760 --> 00:51:38.470
This will be the Viraata, this will be the
complete form of the Primordial Being.

00:51:38.470 --> 00:51:42.960
This is the one I’m telling you about, this
Reflector, The First One.

00:51:42.960 --> 00:51:47.630
The God Almighty has to be reflected, so,
first, let us create, first of all, the Primordial

00:51:47.630 --> 00:51:50.140
Being, the Viraat.

00:51:50.140 --> 00:51:58.940
In the Viraat they created different incarnations.

00:51:58.940 --> 00:52:01.780
Incarnations are not created from human beings.

00:52:01.780 --> 00:52:04.190
I don’t know why people think like that.

00:52:04.190 --> 00:52:05.910
They cannot be created by human beings.

00:52:05.910 --> 00:52:06.950
But they were first created.

00:52:06.950 --> 00:52:12.080
You see, evolution is alright from amoeba
to human beings, but there is no evolution

00:52:12.080 --> 00:52:13.560
for incarnations.

00:52:13.560 --> 00:52:18.660
They are made like that from the very beginning.

00:52:18.660 --> 00:52:29.190
As you have seen in the Viraata, I have shown
you the picture of the Viraat, the three powers

00:52:29.190 --> 00:52:38.540
of Mahakali, Mahalakshmi and Mahasaraswati
met at the Agya Chakra, and there they produced

00:52:38.540 --> 00:52:47.060
two children each – it’s not a story,
is a fact, again – as brothers and sisters.

00:52:47.060 --> 00:52:56.580
And these brothers and sister means the relationship
is of a temporary nature but of a subtler

00:52:56.580 --> 00:52:57.580
temperament.

00:52:57.580 --> 00:53:03.720
And then they were married, inter-communication
took place.

00:53:03.720 --> 00:53:12.570
Mahalakshmi, Mahasaraswati and Mahakali created
all together six children, who were married.

00:53:12.570 --> 00:53:14.810
Inter-marriage took place.

00:53:14.810 --> 00:53:25.100
By that inter-marriage they got an entity
which was a kinetic personality and a potential

00:53:25.100 --> 00:53:28.690
energy within it, such a combination.

00:53:28.690 --> 00:53:32.440
And they placed those incarnations on different
chakras.

00:53:32.440 --> 00:53:39.980
They brought from these, from the top, all
of them were brought from the Agya downward

00:53:39.980 --> 00:53:44.060
and placed onto all the chakras.

00:53:44.060 --> 00:53:50.820
These incarnations, as you know, are placed
on different chakras of the Viraata.

00:53:50.820 --> 00:53:56.130
Many people won’t understand this and won’t
like to hear this also, because human beings

00:53:56.130 --> 00:54:02.840
are so egoistical that they cannot understand
that there is a God, Who is Almighty, Who

00:54:02.840 --> 00:54:07.180
is going to do everything, He has His own
ways of doing it.

00:54:07.180 --> 00:54:11.550
Now, whether I’m telling the Truth or not,
you can verify it on vibrations.

00:54:11.550 --> 00:54:15.220
You can see for yourself how Incarnations
were created.

00:54:15.220 --> 00:54:21.090
And all these Incarnations were placed in
the Viraata state.

00:54:21.090 --> 00:54:34.010
Here, to create the reflection on the other
side, Shiva was removed from the Shakti, as

00:54:34.010 --> 00:54:39.270
it was removed in the beginning and it was
placed on top of the Viraata’s head as the

00:54:39.270 --> 00:54:40.270
Sadashiva’s peetha.

00:54:40.270 --> 00:54:42.180
In the same way, we, too, have a Sadashiva’s
peetha on our head.

00:54:42.180 --> 00:54:44.410
You see, we are the reflection of the reflector.

00:54:44.410 --> 00:54:52.990
So, we, too, have the same style, we, too,
have a Sadahsiva’s peetha on our head.

00:54:52.990 --> 00:54:55.150
He’s also placed here only.

00:54:55.150 --> 00:55:06.619
But when the Kundalini enters into the being,
when he is in the womb of the mother, that

00:55:06.619 --> 00:55:13.410
time this Sadashiva peetha, or we can say,
Sadashiva from this peetha descends into the

00:55:13.410 --> 00:55:14.810
heart.

00:55:14.810 --> 00:55:20.670
And that’s how you hear the first throb
in the heart.

00:55:20.670 --> 00:55:23.820
It is just the same as it happened in the
Viraata.

00:55:23.820 --> 00:55:29.740
But at the vaikuntha stage this was not created,
the second reflector here was not created,

00:55:29.740 --> 00:55:31.300
only the first one.

00:55:31.300 --> 00:55:40.349
So, only the Viraata was created and in His
Being, in the planning stage, first of all,

00:55:40.349 --> 00:55:46.369
these officers, you can say, in charge of
these chakras were created by Adi Shakti.

00:55:46.369 --> 00:55:52.730
God is the witness and She is doing the play
and She creates those chakras.

00:55:52.730 --> 00:55:55.520
In the chakras She places all these deities
to govern.

00:55:55.520 --> 00:56:08.070
Now, there is the existence, there is the
creation, creative force, and there is the

00:56:08.070 --> 00:56:11.570
evolutionary force – all inside the Viraata
state.

00:56:11.570 --> 00:56:16.480
Now, this is at the vaikuntha state, we say,
because this state is on this first reflection.

00:56:16.480 --> 00:56:27.660
It is not in us, or we cannot feel it, the
vaikuntha state, because it is in the first

00:56:27.660 --> 00:56:28.660
thing.

00:56:28.660 --> 00:56:31.310
Then another state was created, then third
was created.

00:56:31.310 --> 00:56:36.360
But the fourth one is the bhavasagara, is
the state at which all of us were born.

00:56:36.360 --> 00:56:43.040
First, in the fourth state…now, can you
think of a four strata personality which is

00:56:43.040 --> 00:56:44.600
facing a mirror?

00:56:44.600 --> 00:56:47.800
Now, which is the first one [that] shows?

00:56:47.800 --> 00:56:48.800
Is the topmost.

00:56:48.800 --> 00:56:50.640
And that’s why the topmost shows is the
bhavasagara.

00:56:50.640 --> 00:56:56.010
But if you can go deep down into your state,
you can feel all the other three.

00:56:56.010 --> 00:56:58.620
But first of all, the one which you can see
and feel it, is the bhavasagara.

00:56:58.620 --> 00:57:00.640
So, you are born in the bhavasagara.

00:57:00.640 --> 00:57:03.430
At this state you are at the bhavasagara state.

00:57:03.430 --> 00:57:11.530
At this bhavasagara state, now, you are created
and you have to evolve.

00:57:11.530 --> 00:57:15.270
At this time the Mahalakshmi power acts to
evolve you.

00:57:15.270 --> 00:57:21.359
You already know how evolutionary things have
taken place but I will tell you how evolution

00:57:21.359 --> 00:57:24.869
has taken place according to our puranas (ancient
scriptures), and which is a fact.

00:57:24.869 --> 00:57:34.580
The Evolution of Man started, first from the
amoeba, you can say; because the life came

00:57:34.580 --> 00:57:37.500
into being into water, as I told you [that]
first the water was created.

00:57:37.500 --> 00:57:42.080
In the water the amino-acids were formed,
amoeba were formed, fishes were formed and

00:57:42.080 --> 00:57:49.230
fishes, when they were formed, they found,
the smaller fishes found it difficult to exist

00:57:49.230 --> 00:57:52.960
because of the bigger fishes were trying to
eat it.

00:57:52.960 --> 00:57:58.390
It comes as a reciprocal thing, they were
absolutely fed up of this destruction that

00:57:58.390 --> 00:57:59.450
was going on.

00:57:59.450 --> 00:58:05.130
At this time, Shri Vishnu Himself, the One
who is the evolutionary force, descended on

00:58:05.130 --> 00:58:08.880
this Earth as the Matsya-Avatara.

00:58:08.880 --> 00:58:12.660
He helped some of the fishes to cross across
the shores.

00:58:12.660 --> 00:58:17.460
By crossing across they had that courage,
She was the leader.

00:58:17.460 --> 00:58:18.860
And then others started crossing across.

00:58:18.860 --> 00:58:22.589
This was the first evolutionary stage which
we know.

00:58:22.589 --> 00:58:27.320
These fishes became reptiles later on; as
you know, in the evolutionary stages that

00:58:27.320 --> 00:58:29.660
they became reptiles.

00:58:29.660 --> 00:58:31.210
But how did they become reptiles?

00:58:31.210 --> 00:58:33.900
There must be someone who must have given
them the lead.

00:58:33.900 --> 00:58:39.950
It was again Shri Vishnu, who came on this
Earth as a Kurma and lots of things were done

00:58:39.950 --> 00:58:45.750
at this time in the vaikuntha stage, before
He came on this Earth as a Kurma Avatara.

00:58:45.750 --> 00:58:51.270
At the vaikuntha stage, when they created
this Earth, when they created, they planned

00:58:51.270 --> 00:58:56.990
this whole Viraata and wanted to create, on
this side of the reflector the whole planning

00:58:56.990 --> 00:59:02.910
and the whole thinking and all that process
brought forth some sort of a waste matter.

00:59:02.910 --> 00:59:06.150
It brought forth the waste matter.

00:59:06.150 --> 00:59:11.360
This waste matter got contaminated or, we
can say, got stagnated on to one side which

00:59:11.360 --> 00:59:16.532
was neglected somehow, and through it started
coming out some satanic forces and there was

00:59:16.532 --> 00:59:20.630
a big fight between the satanic forces and
the good forces.

00:59:20.630 --> 00:59:25.030
It actually happened in the third stage, not
at the vaikuntha stage, but at the third stage,

00:59:25.030 --> 00:59:28.420
because when the planning started, the working
out started, these satanic forces started

00:59:28.420 --> 00:59:29.420
working out.

00:59:29.420 --> 00:59:31.410
Now, people may say, “Why God created satanic
forces?”

00:59:31.410 --> 00:59:38.090
He did not, but eventually they turned out
to be because at the second stage, when some

00:59:38.090 --> 00:59:39.560
of the Devas, who were created.

00:59:39.560 --> 00:59:43.960
Again, they were not evolved people, they
were created, Devas, in charge of all these

00:59:43.960 --> 00:59:48.020
elements and all the working, you see, you
have to create also officers or people who

00:59:48.020 --> 00:59:49.760
have to go in the field and work out.

00:59:49.760 --> 00:59:54.040
All these Devas and Devatas: out of their
working, what happened [is] that they got

00:59:54.040 --> 00:59:56.710
lost, some of them, and became satanic forces.

00:59:56.710 --> 01:00:01.770
Sort of a waste-product came in, and with
that waste-product, satanic forces started

01:00:01.770 --> 01:00:08.790
and they acted in such a way that there was
a war during the Kurma-Avatara between Rakshasas

01:00:08.790 --> 01:00:10.150
and the Suras, as they call it.

01:00:10.150 --> 01:00:14.430
So, the good people who were in charge of
the elements, all the working in the office

01:00:14.430 --> 01:00:17.440
of God started fighting with the satanic forces.

01:00:17.440 --> 01:00:24.410
At that time, He Himself worked out this and
you know what happened in the amrut-mantan

01:00:24.410 --> 01:00:28.960
which took place, and this is, – people
don’t understand how can the amrut-mantan

01:00:28.960 --> 01:00:30.810
take place in the bhavasagara, – it did
not.

01:00:30.810 --> 01:00:36.180
It took place at a stage which is not bhavasagara.

01:00:36.180 --> 01:00:38.510
At the bhavasagara it did not take place.

01:00:38.510 --> 01:00:41.330
Now, we are at the bhavasagara state.

01:00:41.330 --> 01:00:45.073
At the bhavasagara state the same Kurma, the
same one took birth and came on this Earth

01:00:45.073 --> 01:00:48.940
and gave us a understanding how to become
a proper reptile.

01:00:48.940 --> 01:00:50.260
Like that we grew up.

01:00:50.260 --> 01:00:53.460
So, the whole thing will take too much time,
I need not go into that.

01:00:53.460 --> 01:00:55.710
But, ultimately, a human being was created.

01:00:55.710 --> 01:01:01.180
All this is done by Mahalakshmi power, which
has acted through Vishnu, which I have told

01:01:01.180 --> 01:01:09.010
you how evolution has taken place, how you
are made.

01:01:09.010 --> 01:01:11.190
Now, what is going to happen?

01:01:11.190 --> 01:01:13.750
You reach this point, up to this point, till
Christ came in.

01:01:13.750 --> 01:01:17.890
Christ was also an incarnation and his Mother
was nobody else but Radhaji Herself, the Mahalakshmi.

01:01:17.890 --> 01:01:21.380
And they brought forth up to this stage the
human beings.

01:01:21.380 --> 01:01:24.349
After this, now, what man has to become?

01:01:24.349 --> 01:01:32.420
– is to enter into a state where he becomes
nirvichar, means there is no more the consciousness

01:01:32.420 --> 01:01:35.760
of the bhavasagara, but you go little beyond
it.

01:01:35.760 --> 01:01:45.720
From this stage you dive into a state of Universal
Unconscious, as they call it, it’s nothing

01:01:45.720 --> 01:01:49.950
but the same power which exists here, which
is a synthesis of all the three powers, is

01:01:49.950 --> 01:01:51.950
the synthesis of all the three powers.

01:01:51.950 --> 01:01:53.410
That is the Adi Shakti’s power.

01:01:53.410 --> 01:01:58.220
Adi Shakti’s power is all-pervading, exists
everywhere, but we never feel it otherwise.

01:01:58.220 --> 01:01:59.220
Why?

01:01:59.220 --> 01:02:00.630
Because we are very grossly placed.

01:02:00.630 --> 01:02:06.420
We can say, that a tube, which has got, say
four layers, out of which it can only use

01:02:06.420 --> 01:02:10.760
the outer tube, because the inner tubes are
all closed.

01:02:10.760 --> 01:02:15.859
When the innermost tube is opened out, you
become absolutely Self-realised, but when

01:02:15.859 --> 01:02:20.270
even the second tube is opened out, you can
feel the all-pervading force of God Almighty,

01:02:20.270 --> 01:02:24.410
which is, we call it as Sampovapi achetan.

01:02:24.410 --> 01:02:28.859
But it is no more achetan (unconscious) for
you because you are conscious of it.

01:02:28.859 --> 01:02:31.359
That is how you start your dialogue with God.

01:02:31.359 --> 01:02:36.359
What happens is that here, the reflection
here, the reflector, that is reflecting work,

01:02:36.359 --> 01:02:38.940
from here you ascend into this part.

01:02:38.940 --> 01:02:41.530
You ascend onto this part.

01:02:41.530 --> 01:02:46.070
You do not become this but you ascend into
this area.

01:02:46.070 --> 01:02:48.650
From here you ascend into this area.

01:02:48.650 --> 01:02:55.520
And this area is filled with the all-pervading
power of Adi Shakti.

01:02:55.520 --> 01:03:01.230
Till you reach to this stage, you have to
go up to this stage of an incarnation, which,

01:03:01.230 --> 01:03:02.760
of course, is a big gap.

01:03:02.760 --> 01:03:08.520
But I can say that Mahavira and Buddha, both
of them rose to that height.

01:03:08.520 --> 01:03:09.580
But look at their disciples!

01:03:09.580 --> 01:03:13.410
For example, Buddha’s disciples, they have
decried Shiva, they have decried all the Gods

01:03:13.410 --> 01:03:15.920
and Goddesses, I mean as if they did not know
much about it.

01:03:15.920 --> 01:03:22.130
And the way they have shown in certain statues
– that a Goddess is standing on top of a

01:03:22.130 --> 01:03:26.260
Shiva and a Parvati and is trying to kill;
She is hitting Shri Ganesha and this is something

01:03:26.260 --> 01:03:27.260
so non-sensical.

01:03:27.260 --> 01:03:32.670
I mean, they completely killed the image of
One United Force, acting the whole thing,

01:03:32.670 --> 01:03:35.030
in One united idea, with One united mind.

01:03:35.030 --> 01:03:39.980
Only whenever they had not united, they became
Rakshasas and formed the satanic force.

01:03:39.980 --> 01:03:44.300
As I told you it’s a very, very difficult
subject and I’ve tried to handle it in English,

01:03:44.300 --> 01:03:45.300
is even worse.

01:03:45.300 --> 01:03:49.750
So, I’ve tried my level best to do it, but
still if you have any questions, anything,

01:03:49.750 --> 01:03:53.420
you can ask me, some time, you can write to
me, we can find it out.

01:03:53.420 --> 01:03:57.200
For tomorrow…Now, this is the only thing
is, I wanted to tell you about this, that

01:03:57.200 --> 01:03:58.660
now you have got thoughtless awareness, no
doubt.

01:03:58.660 --> 01:04:02.750
Most of you have got thoughtless awareness,
you have got vibrations, but you have to jump

01:04:02.750 --> 01:04:03.750
into Nirvikalpa.

01:04:03.750 --> 01:04:04.750
Nirvikalpa.

01:04:04.750 --> 01:04:08.339
And [to] that you have to jump through deep
meditation and through deep exposure.

01:04:08.339 --> 01:04:13.160
Otherwise, you see, it is no use only having
this little state of Nirvichara, you have

01:04:13.160 --> 01:04:14.160
to jump into Nirvikalpa.

01:04:14.160 --> 01:04:19.160
That is a stage, little, as I’ve told you
here, that a little ahead of this reflector,

01:04:19.160 --> 01:04:20.160
you have moved.

01:04:20.160 --> 01:04:22.460
But still you are going up and down, so many
of you.

01:04:22.460 --> 01:04:27.071
This is a state known as satori in the Zen
system of religion, they call it as satori:

01:04:27.071 --> 01:04:29.460
where, you see, if a person is going up and
down, is catching, doing this, that.

01:04:29.460 --> 01:04:31.089
This stage has to be overcome.

01:04:31.089 --> 01:04:34.120
Then you go to the Nirvikalpa state.

01:04:34.120 --> 01:04:35.910
At the end of the Nirvikalpa state you just
don’t catch much.

01:04:35.910 --> 01:04:37.370
You are not bothered.

01:04:37.370 --> 01:04:40.930
So far, I haven’t met any human being like
that.

01:04:40.930 --> 01:04:47.520
You see, I have seen very great saints and
realised people and I can say that they are

01:04:47.520 --> 01:04:52.710
definitely Self-realised, they are even controlling
nature, some of them do, but still they catch

01:04:52.710 --> 01:04:54.890
on their chakras, is something surprising.

01:04:54.890 --> 01:04:59.810
But, you see, human beings are like that,
they’ll go on catching and again, perhaps,

01:04:59.810 --> 01:05:04.080
they jump into the third state of Self-realisation
completely, but they are again in a satori

01:05:04.080 --> 01:05:06.560
state and they come back and go back and,
like that, may be.

01:05:06.560 --> 01:05:11.250
But I have seen that, so far, I have not met
one human being whom I will say he is fully

01:05:11.250 --> 01:05:13.180
Self-realised, who doesn’t catch.

01:05:13.180 --> 01:05:17.340
Except for me, I find, everybody is catching.

01:05:17.340 --> 01:05:19.680
It’s most surprising.

01:05:19.680 --> 01:05:22.580
But when you don’t catch – what happens,
when you don’t catch?

01:05:22.580 --> 01:05:24.520
Actually, this is a state rather difficult
to achieve.

01:05:24.520 --> 01:05:30.740
But if you don’t catch, if you think you
don’t catch – how you should do it ?- is

01:05:30.740 --> 01:05:34.220
to see this way: that if, supposing, you are
catching Agya, maybe.

01:05:34.220 --> 01:05:38.190
You must know that when you are catching your
Agya, you should not think you are catching

01:05:38.190 --> 01:05:42.220
your Agya, but you should think that you are
gathering a force here to combat the another

01:05:42.220 --> 01:05:43.220
person.

01:05:43.220 --> 01:05:44.220
If you can do like that.

01:05:44.220 --> 01:05:48.930
Supposing you are catching on the Vishuddhi
chakra, instead of thinking that you are catching

01:05:48.930 --> 01:05:53.270
on Vishuddhi chakra and getting upset about
it, if you start thinking that this is a force

01:05:53.270 --> 01:05:56.240
you are accumulating just to counterbalance
his Vishuddhi chakra.

01:05:56.240 --> 01:05:59.220
Then, I think, it will work out better.

01:05:59.220 --> 01:06:03.710
That’s why I always say that: extend your
hands to others and see for yourself.

01:06:03.710 --> 01:06:07.359
This has helped many people because if they
catch on Agya and if they give vibrations

01:06:07.359 --> 01:06:08.790
to somebody who is Agya caught, they find
they are released.

01:06:08.790 --> 01:06:11.960
Such things are happening to very few but
it’s happening.

01:06:11.960 --> 01:06:15.700
So, this is what you can try: that don’t
think you are catching but you should think:

01:06:15.700 --> 01:06:19.890
a force has been accumulated to expel the
Agya of another person who is facing you.

01:06:19.890 --> 01:06:23.340
In the beginning, of course, it’s a very,
very slow process, but gradually you can do

01:06:23.340 --> 01:06:26.450
it and only people who start giving others.

01:06:26.450 --> 01:06:30.330
This is a collective thinking, is a collective
thinking: that, supposing, now you can say

01:06:30.330 --> 01:06:35.470
like that, that if, supposing, there is a
malaria attack on Me, then My own blood, My

01:06:35.470 --> 01:06:38.190
own blood cells are trying to combat it.

01:06:38.190 --> 01:06:39.230
And they are combating it.

01:06:39.230 --> 01:06:42.359
You see, if I give in, if I give in, then
I become malarious.

01:06:42.359 --> 01:06:44.180
But if I do not give in, I become victorious.

01:06:44.180 --> 01:06:50.330
In the same way, if you could think this way
while giving vibrations: that if you catch

01:06:50.330 --> 01:06:54.839
it is actually a force being accumulated into
you and then you have to give it, then you

01:06:54.839 --> 01:06:58.250
are going to be much faster than all the munis
put together, I can tell you.

01:06:58.250 --> 01:07:01.470
But that thinking is rather difficult for
human beings, because once they catch, they

01:07:01.470 --> 01:07:04.260
get little worried, “I’m catching,”
they start taking out their own.

01:07:04.260 --> 01:07:08.270
If you don’t take out your own and go all
out to give it to others, it will work out

01:07:08.270 --> 01:07:09.270
better.

01:07:09.270 --> 01:07:12.720
And this I’ve been, I’ve experimented
with one or two people, I’m saying, and

01:07:12.720 --> 01:07:13.720
it has worked.

01:07:13.720 --> 01:07:14.800
Everybody does not have that capacity.

01:07:14.800 --> 01:07:18.950
So, gradually you rise, because you are just
now newly born children, you have still to

01:07:18.950 --> 01:07:21.720
grow, you have to grow more.

01:07:21.720 --> 01:07:25.030
You might be learned, you might be knowing
a lot, that doesn’t mean, as far as your

01:07:25.030 --> 01:07:27.810
spirituality is concerned, you have just have
come out of your satori state, some of you,

01:07:27.810 --> 01:07:29.980
and some of you are still in the satori state.

01:07:29.980 --> 01:07:32.230
So, be careful about it.

01:07:32.230 --> 01:07:36.170
I would like to meet you again, perhaps, after
two years, I don’t know when.

01:07:36.170 --> 01:07:39.130
Tomorrow we are having a meditation here,
then I won’t speak much.

01:07:39.130 --> 01:07:40.560
Tomorrow we have a meditation.

01:07:40.560 --> 01:07:45.540
We have a meditation centre here, where you
should go and meet, when you meet in a group

01:07:45.540 --> 01:07:51.410
then it is a samuhik, is a group activity,
I will be there.

01:07:51.410 --> 01:07:57.130
You’ll be surprised that my vibrations cannot
be felt anywhere so much as they can be felt

01:07:57.130 --> 01:08:00.490
in a group, about which I know that such and
such group is working here.

01:08:00.490 --> 01:08:03.590
So, we have already three groups which are
working in Delhi.

01:08:03.590 --> 01:08:05.710
And they are made quite closer to the places.

01:08:05.710 --> 01:08:09.060
After all, we must know that we don’t have
to go to Himalayas, as people went down, we

01:08:09.060 --> 01:08:10.190
don’t have to do all these things.

01:08:10.190 --> 01:08:13.950
Only thing we have to go is to a place which
is very much closer to us, it has been brought

01:08:13.950 --> 01:08:15.320
to our doors.

01:08:15.320 --> 01:08:21.620
The whole thing has been brought to your doors:
the knowledge, the vibrations, the realisation

01:08:21.620 --> 01:08:22.930
and everything is made so easy.

01:08:22.930 --> 01:08:23.930
It’s made easy….

01:08:23.930 --> 01:08:26.609
But it should not mean that we should take
it for granted.

01:08:26.609 --> 01:08:31.339
It has been made easy through a very, very
great tapasya on my part, I should say.

01:08:31.339 --> 01:08:35.089
In many ages I’ve been living now for thousands
of years and I’ve been working it out on

01:08:35.089 --> 01:08:40.190
so many human beings and so many things and,
at long last, I’ve been able to find out

01:08:40.190 --> 01:08:43.830
most of the permutations and combinations
of most of the human beings and that’s how

01:08:43.830 --> 01:08:46.359
it has been worked out in such a large mass-scale.

01:08:46.359 --> 01:08:49.920
It would not have been possible if I had not
worked it out in that way.

01:08:49.920 --> 01:08:54.210
And that’s how if it has worked out it has
to click with most of the people except for

01:08:54.210 --> 01:09:00.460
one type is very, very difficult, I must say,
those who are bound to people who are rakshasas.

01:09:00.460 --> 01:09:03.819
If they are born rakshasas and if your head
has touched their feet, it’s a very difficult

01:09:03.819 --> 01:09:04.819
thing.

01:09:04.819 --> 01:09:06.989
So, I would warn you, that before you touch
feet of anybody, you’d be careful about

01:09:06.989 --> 01:09:07.989
it.

01:09:07.989 --> 01:09:08.989
May God bless you all!

01:09:08.989 --> 01:09:13.270
It’s already very late for all of you and
such a difficult subject to be brought to

01:09:13.270 --> 01:09:16.370
such a short time, it’s very difficult.

01:09:16.370 --> 01:09:21.030
I hope to write some book on Sahaja Yoga:
‘I hope’, I am saying, because, so far,

01:09:21.030 --> 01:09:22.109
I’ve never written any book.

01:09:22.109 --> 01:09:24.950
[I’m] trying to write some book, but before
that some other people are writing.

01:09:24.950 --> 01:09:27.920
I hope, I may be able to write something.

01:09:27.920 --> 01:09:31.440
In any case, you try not to bother too much
about these things.

01:09:31.440 --> 01:09:35.880
This is not so important as your own realisation
and your own ascent [because] the whole knowledge

01:09:35.880 --> 01:09:37.029
will be dawned upon you.

01:09:37.029 --> 01:09:38.730
You don’t have to bother!

01:09:38.730 --> 01:09:41.730
Every word now you read, you will have a meaning
about it and you will understand.

01:09:41.730 --> 01:09:45.670
The first thing is that you must get your
realisation, second thing is you must ascend.

01:09:45.670 --> 01:09:48.980
You must ascend much more and give more time
to this.

01:09:48.980 --> 01:09:50.410
Do not take it for granted.

01:09:50.410 --> 01:09:52.680
It is a very important thing which you should
do.

01:09:52.680 --> 01:09:54.969
After all there are other things, they are
important.

01:09:54.969 --> 01:09:57.820
But this is the most important thing which
has to be done.

01:09:57.820 --> 01:10:01.480
By God’s grace, if it works out I’ll be
very happy.

01:10:01.480 --> 01:10:07.060
As it is, I’m extremely happy because in
none of my lives I’ve been able to give

01:10:07.060 --> 01:10:09.130
realisations to so many people.

01:10:09.130 --> 01:10:11.460
So as it is, I am over-satisfied with Myself.

01:10:11.460 --> 01:10:15.190
But as far as you are concerned, you should
not be satisfied, you should ask for more

01:10:15.190 --> 01:10:17.940
and more and more and it will be granted.

01:10:17.940 --> 01:10:20.690
Because you are the people who are on the
stage, you are created for this purpose.

01:10:20.690 --> 01:10:22.340
One has to do it.

01:10:22.340 --> 01:10:24.449
God has to do it.

01:10:24.449 --> 01:10:29.489
If He does not do it, He cannot fulfil His
own desires.

01:10:29.489 --> 01:10:31.340
And His Creation, He is not going to destroy.

01:10:31.340 --> 01:10:31.469
May God bless you!
